WEBVTT

00:00:01.500 --> 00:00:02.650
It's story time.

00:00:03.492 --> 00:00:05.292
Settle back, and I'll begin.

00:00:06.643 --> 00:00:11.508
Once upon a time, a mother duck
sat patiently on her nest of eggs,

00:00:11.532 --> 00:00:13.265
waiting for them to hatch.

00:00:13.953 --> 00:00:17.222
And then one day, she felt
something move beneath her.

00:00:17.246 --> 00:00:18.555
Crack, crack!

00:00:19.397 --> 00:00:23.813
Filled with happiness, she watched
as her eggs hatched one by one.

00:00:25.726 --> 00:00:27.917
I don't know about you,
but when I was little,

00:00:27.941 --> 00:00:31.186
story time was always
one of my favorite parts of the day.